###### PDFConverter ######

Function: Takes all multiplots in files produced by multifits.cc and outputs their pdfs.

Input/Execution:

Must be used with root as there is no main method:

.x PDFConverter.cc(std::string var)

var: Variable whose plots are to be accessed, i.e. .x PDFConverter("x") will take all the graphs in "MultipleFits_x.root" 
     and output their pdf versions.
